[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":195},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F":171,"related:\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F":180},"\u002Fen\u002Fvscode\u002F2023\u002F10\u002F26\u002Fvscode-vue-custom-component-syntax-highlight-fix\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":155,"date":156,"description":24,"extension":157,"lang":158,"meta":159,"navigation":160,"path":161,"readingMinutes":162,"seo":163,"standalone":164,"stem":165,"tags":166,"tldr":168,"updated":156,"url":169,"__hash__":170},"content\u002FVSCode\u002FVSCode-上-Vue-自訂元件失去高亮.md","VSCode 上 Vue 自訂元件失去高亮","54606935",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":150},"minimark",[11,18,22,25,28,31,37,40,46,49,52,63,70,73,76,125,138,143,146],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":6,"src":17},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fvue_components_highlighting\u002Fisray_notarray_green_cute_bug_is_animation_style_637ff80c-9b21-4937-8954-5dd5a5cd9f7e.png",[19,20,21],"h2",{"id":21},"前言",[12,23,24],{},"最近開發發現 Volar 的自訂元件高亮功能好像怪怪的，所以記錄一下原因。",[19,26,27],{"id":27},"問題",[12,29,30],{},"通常來講，我們在 Vue 的時候只要是自定義的元件都會是綠色高亮，這樣的好處是可以讓我們快速看到這個元件是不是自定義的，像是下面這樣：",[12,32,33],{},[15,34],{"alt":35,"src":36},"高亮","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fvue_components_highlighting\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-10-26%2011.05.05.png",[12,38,39],{},"但是不知道為什麼在某次更新 VSCode 之後全部變成了這樣...",[12,41,42],{},[15,43],{"alt":44,"src":45},"失去高亮","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fvscode\u002Fvue_components_highlighting\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202023-10-26%2011.07.26.png",[12,47,48],{},"所以就要來記錄一下原因了",[19,50,51],{"id":51},"障礙排除",[12,53,54,55,62],{},"第一直覺我就先去找了 Vue 官方所做的 ",[56,57,61],"a",{"href":58,"rel":59},"https:\u002F\u002Fmarketplace.visualstudio.com\u002Fitems?itemName=Vue.volar",[60],"nofollow","Vue Language Features (Volar)"," 套件，我以為是這個套件更新出現了 Bug，所以嘗試移除並重新安裝發現無效，後又找到以下這一篇 Issues：",[12,64,65],{},[56,66,69],{"href":67,"rel":68},"https:\u002F\u002Fgithub.com\u002Fvuejs\u002Flanguage-tools\u002Fissues\u002F1158",[60],"Syntax highlighting seems different from the previous version",[12,71,72],{},"就可以確定有人是跟我一樣的，但是這個問題官方在去年就已經修正了，所以我就去看看自己的版本是不是最新的，結果發現我是最新的版本，所以就不是這個問題了 QQ",[12,74,75],{},"接下來我就開始懷疑該不會是 VSCode 某次更新發神經又加了什麼或者改了什麼設定吧？所以我就嘗試去找 VSCode 的設定，結果發現了這個設定：",[77,78,83],"pre",{"className":79,"code":80,"language":81,"meta":82,"style":82},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{\n  \u002F\u002F ... 其他設定\n  \"editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled\": false,\n}\n","json","",[84,85,86,95,102,119],"code",{"__ignoreMap":82},[87,88,91],"span",{"class":89,"line":90},"line",1,[87,92,94],{"class":93},"sMAXC","{\n",[87,96,98],{"class":89,"line":97},2,[87,99,101],{"class":100},"sQrFR","  \u002F\u002F ... 其他設定\n",[87,103,105,109,112,116],{"class":89,"line":104},3,[87,106,108],{"class":107},"sKpQp","  \"editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled\"",[87,110,111],{"class":93},": ",[87,113,115],{"class":114},"sCcAr","false",[87,117,118],{"class":93},",\n",[87,120,122],{"class":89,"line":121},4,[87,123,124],{"class":93},"}\n",[12,126,127,128,130,131,134,135,137],{},"這個設定是專門控制是否會為支援的語言顯示的選項，但不知道為什麼被設定為 ",[84,129,115],{}," 了 Orz，將它改完 ",[84,132,133],{},"true"," 就正常了（你可以刪除，反正預設為 ",[84,136,133],{},"）",[12,139,140],{},[15,141],{"alt":142,"src":36},"恢復正常",[12,144,145],{},"如果這個問題沒修正的話，其實在開發上跟維護上真的滿困擾的，因為人就是視覺動物咩...",[147,148,149],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .sQrFR, html code.shiki .sQrFR{--shiki-default:#BDC4CC}html pre.shiki code .sKpQp, html code.shiki .sKpQp{--shiki-default:#72F088}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":82,"searchDepth":97,"depth":97,"links":151},[152,153,154],{"id":21,"depth":97,"text":21},{"id":27,"depth":97,"text":27},{"id":51,"depth":97,"text":51},"VSCode","2023-10-26 11:03:07","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fvscode\u002Fvscode-vue-yuan","1",{"title":6,"description":24},false,"VSCode\u002FVSCode-上-Vue-自訂元件失去高亮",[51,155,167],"Vue",null,"\u002Fvscode\u002F20231026\u002F54606935\u002F","c73zC0A6BQJ55jstTsjJjYUd-WO5r7TcN7pE5Op7ZG0",{"newer":172,"older":176},{"url":173,"title":174,"date":175},"\u002Fother\u002F20231029\u002F4161770695\u002F","首頁總是不更新，關於被 Service Workers 雷的這件事","2023-10-29 00:12:47",{"url":177,"title":178,"date":179},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231024\u002F1839693229\u002F","Mac 開啟專案時，自動使用 nvm use 切換到專案的 Node 版本","2023-10-24 16:00:52",[181,185,190],{"url":182,"title":183,"date":184,"readingMinutes":162},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20250424\u002F4258825567\u002F","VSCode 找不到 Git，安裝它或使用 \"git.path\" 設置","2025-04-24 09:52:23",{"url":186,"title":187,"date":188,"readingMinutes":189},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20240908\u002F3488366595\u002F","GitHub Copilot 好難用？說不定是你不懂 Copilot 之技巧全攻略不藏私！","2024-09-08 13:06:00","5",{"url":191,"title":192,"date":193,"readingMinutes":194},"\u002Fvscode\u002F20230921\u002F1985180173\u002F","Visual Studio Code 自訂折疊區塊","2023-09-21 09:43:55","2",1784011737246]